reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cool and calming
reviews.reviewText: This is a necklace made for those who prefer understated beauty. The pendant is well-polished, with a surface that’s smooth like a worry stone. Mine is a light, soothing green that matches the pale-ish gold of the setting and chain. The spring ring clasp is easy to use. I like this necklace enough that I’d be happy to wear it every day, and I could — it would go with almost any outfit.Part of what makes this feel worth the price for me is the gift packaging, which (no exaggeration) made me happy for a second when I opened the mailer envelope. It feels pulled together instead of thrown together, and that matters. The box is darn stylish compared to a generic jewelry gift box — flat and low-profile, with a pattern like birch bark on the outside and a hint of sparkle on the inside. The jewelry pouch has a substantial, suede-y texture, and the button over the snap closure is covered. With. Fabric! (It’s the little things, seriously.)Note that my package didn’t contain the maintenance and care card or the cleaning cloth that I see in another review, possibly because I got the gold-plated version, which shouldn’t tarnish like the sterling silver version.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Delicate and very giftable
reviews.reviewText: This is a beautiful and delicate piece of jewelry. I would not hesitate to gift this to my daughter or my friend. It is a very delicate looking piece, and it comes in a very giftable presentation. The jade in the good fortune circle that I ordered is a medium green. I like the card that comes enclosed with a description of the stone properties. As seen in other posted photos, it comes in a nice little box, and it includes a soft pouch for storing and keeping it undamaged. It also includes a soft cleaning cloth to remove skin oils an keep the silver clean and shiny for a longer period of time. The original price is a bit high, but if you can take advantage of the discount coupon, it is a deal. Very nice and giftable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Petite Pendant, Beautiful Colour & Style
reviews.reviewText: I have been drawn to jade--both jadeite and nephrite--since I can remember, and I chose this because it is a smaller and somewhat more delicate pendant than most I've come across. The colour is always a bit of a gamble when acquiring jade online (so many variations and shades!), so I was delighted when this arrived and I unpacked a pendant with a soft, classic jade green colour and a beautiful glassy sheen.The sterling chain is adjustable and easy to put on, and the necklace came gorgeously gift boxed with an information card, care directions, polishing cloth, and faux suede snapped pouch. I'm thoroughly impressed, and happy to recommend this to anyone who is looking for a lovely, high quality jade pendant.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Pendant Is Pretty, But Pale
reviews.reviewText: This pendant would be great for the young, but definitely looks inexpensive. The jade is nearly white, the chain looks flat and flimsy, but the presentation box is very nice. Perfect for a pre-teen/tween.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It's a pretty pendant. The jade is a pretty dull color and quite small. It is however quite smooth to the touch. The length is perfect. The metal does seem a tad fake looking being so bright. Will update if it starts turning another color after a few months.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My new favorite piece of jewelry
reviews.reviewText: I ordered the sterling silver Four Leaf Clover style pendant, and it is so beautiful. The listing said that the jade stones vary in color, so I was curious what shade I would received. I'm so pleased with it! It's a medium green, though it seems to change color depending on what it's next too. Sometimes it looks like it has a hint of teal, which is gorgeous. The pendant is well made and hangs on a delicate silver chain with an extender. It comes beautifully boxed and ready for gift giving, but I think you'll want to keep it for yourself!

reviews.reviewText: Pictures do not do justice. The necklace is so much prettier in person. The stone seems good quality as well. I love the box it came in. It was pretty much ready to give as a gift. I gave this necklace to my daughter as a mom daughter Valentine’s Day gift. She loved it!! I recommend! ;)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice chain; Very pretty smooth stone
reviews.reviewText: I love this necklace. I’ve always loved jade and so it caught my eye. When it came it was in a nice box with a protective bag and care instructions.The necklace itself has a nice silver chain with a decent clasp. I don’t have any issues putting it on myself. I wish the chain was just the tiniest bit longer but that’s just a nitpick from me and you can always put the pendant on a longer chain. The stone is very nice and I’m glad I ended up with a stone that’s on the greener side. I know the listing says there’s a chance you can get a paler stone so I’m happy mine is more green.
